---
const { missingPrice = 0, missingContext = 0, missingOfficial = 0, total = 0 } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="rounded-lg border border-amber-300/25 bg-amber-300/10 p-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-amber-50">
  <p class="font-semibold">缺失字段说明</p>
  <p class="mt-2">对比页只解释已有字段，不补写未知信息。`暂无数据`、`官方未披露`、`Artificial Analysis 未披露` 和 `待核验` 表示当前资料源未披露或尚未接入，不代表模型一定不支持。</p>
  <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs">
    <span class="rounded-md border border-amber-300/35 px-2 py-1">价格待补公开资料：{missingPrice} / {total}</span>
    <span class="rounded-md border border-amber-300/35 px-2 py-1">上下文待补公开资料：{missingContext} / {total}</span>
    <span class="rounded-md border border-amber-300/35 px-2 py-1">官方链接待补公开资料：{missingOfficial} / {total}</span>
  </div>
</section>
